# OpenDataLoader PDF

![Pre-release](https://img.shields.io/badge/Pre--release-FFA500&logo=github)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/opendataloader-pdf.svg)](https://pypi.org/project/opendataloader-pdf/)
